title: Standford coach Tara VanDerveer's pursuit of 1,000
description: With Stanford women's basketball coach Tara VanDerveer on the brink of becoming the third Division 1 coach ever to reach 1,000 career wins, here's a look at her milestone wins and accomplishments along the way.

author: janny hu, mike massa, lucio villa
